        <div class="lp-image__content">
         <span class="lp-lazy-image" style="max-width:118px"><span class="lp-lazy-image__content" style="padding-top:calc(33/118*100%)"><img src="https://s1.wp.com/wp-content/themes/h4/landing/marketing/pages/hp-2022-oct/media/desktop/jetpack-logo.svg" loading="lazy" alt="Jetpack logo" width="118" height="33"></span></span>
        </div>
       </div> <span class="lp-block lp-spacer lp-spacer--size-0"></span> 
       <h2 class="wp-block-heading has-huge-font-size">Take your site with&nbsp;you</h2> 
       <p class="lp-width-480">The <strong>Jetpack App</strong> gives you everything you need to&nbsp;create, manage, and grow your site—from&nbsp;anywhere.</p> 
       <div class="lp-block lp-flex-utility lp-flex-utility--has-justify-content lp-flex-utility--has-flex-wrap lp-flex-utility--has-column-gap lp-flex-utility--has-row-gap lp-margin-top-3 lp-margin-bottom-0" style="justify-content:flex-start;flex-wrap:wrap;column-gap:var(--lp-pad-1);row-gap:var(--lp-pad-1)"> 
        <div class="lp-block lp-content lp-content--text-alignment lp-content--text-alignment-left lp-flex-item lp-flex-item--shrink">
         <div class="lp-block lp-mobile-badge lp-mobile-badge--type-apple-app-store is-style-mobile-badge-white">
          <a class="lp-mobile-badge__link" href="https://apps.apple.com/app/apple-store/id1565481562?ct=wp.com--empty-campaign&amp;mt=8&amp;pt=299112"><span class="lp-mobile-badge__content">
            <svg class="lp-mobile-badge__content__icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewbox="0 0 18 23" aria-hidden="true">
