            </svg><span class="lp-mobile-badge__content__label"><span class="lp-mobile-badge__line lp-mobile-badge__line--is-top">Download on the</span> <span class="lp-mobile-badge__line lp-mobile-badge__line--is-bottom">App Store</span></span></span></a>
